				Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.
			</p>
			<a href="#" class="btn-outline">
				<Download size={16} /> Scarica Articolo Completo
			</a>
		</details>

		<details>
			<summary><strong>Giulia Bianchi - Il Dialetto di Damasco</strong></summary>
			<p>
				Uno studio approfondito sulle variazioni fonetiche nel dialetto damasceno contemporaneo...
			</p>
			<a href="#" class="btn-outline">
				<Download size={16} /> Scarica Articolo Completo
			</a>
		</details>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	/* Optional inline styles for specific iconic alignments if needed */
	.inline-icon {
		vertical-align: middle;
		margin-right: 4px;
	}
    /* Flex utility since we are avoiding utility classes but need alignment */
    .flex {
        display: flex;
    }
    .items-center {
        align-items: center;
    }
    .gap-2 {
        gap: 0.5rem;
    }
</style>
